19324#elif defined(__CUDA_API_PER_THREAD_DEFAULT_STREAM)
19325static inline CUresult cuGetProcAddress_ptsz(const char *symbol, void **funcPtr, int driverVersion, cuuint64_t flags) {
19326 const int procAddressMask = (CU_GET_PROC_ADDRESS_LEGACY_STREAM|
19327 CU_GET_PROC_ADDRESS_PER_THREAD_DEFAULT_STREAM);
19328 if ((flags & procAddressMask) == 0) {
19329 flags |= CU_GET_PROC_ADDRESS_PER_THREAD_DEFAULT_STREAM;
19330 }
19331 return cuGetProcAddress(symbol, funcPtr, driverVersion, flags);
19332}
19333#define cuGetProcAddress cuGetProcAddress_ptsz
19334#endif
